Mail/Sender/Easy.pm version 0.0.5
================================

See
 perldoc Mail::Sender::Easy
for more info

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

or
 perl -MCPAN -e 'install Mail::Sender::Easy;'

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

Mail::Sender

